      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Collection consists of black and white glass lantern slides of Western and Southern Asia. Entries for countries, some of which have older place names, include Afghanistan, Bali (Indonesia), Ceylon (Sri Lanka), Formosa (Taiwan), Java (Indonesia), Korea, and Siam (Thailand).</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_arr1">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged alphabetically by medium. Further sub-divided by location or chronological period, and if known, by individual artist name.</p>  
      </arrangement>
